import React from "react"; import { ShieldCheckIcon, HomeIcon, UserGroupIcon, DevicePhoneMobileIcon, ExclamationTriangleIcon, } from "@heroicons/react/24/outline"; function SafetyTips() { const safetyCategories = [ { title: "General Safety", icon: ShieldCheckIcon, tips: [ "Always be aware of your surroundings", "Trust your instincts - if something feels wrong, it probably is", "Keep emergency numbers saved in your phone", "Share your location with trusted contacts when traveling", "Avoid displaying expensive items in public", ], }, { title: "Home Safety", icon: HomeIcon, tips: [ "Install proper lighting around your property", "Keep doors and windows locked when not at home", "Install security cameras and alarms", "Get to know your neighbors", "Keep emergency exits clear and accessible", ], }, { title: "Public Safety", icon: UserGroupIcon, tips: [ "Stay in well-lit and populated areas", "Avoid using headphones in public places", "Keep your phone charged and accessible", "Be cautious when using ATMs", "Report suspicious activities to authorities", ], }, { title: "Digital Safety", icon: DevicePhoneMobileIcon, tips: [ "Use strong, unique passwords", "Enable two-factor authentication", "Be cautious when sharing personal information online", "Keep your devices and apps updated", "Use secure networks for sensitive transactions", ], }, { title: "Emergency Preparedness", icon: ExclamationTriangleIcon, tips: [ "Know the emergency numbers for your area", "Keep a first-aid kit at home and in your car", "Have an emergency evacuation plan", "Keep important documents in a safe place", "Learn basic first aid and CPR", ], }, ]; return (

Safety Tips and Guidelines

{safetyCategories.map((category) => (

{category.title}

    {category.tips.map((tip, index) => (
  • • {tip}
    • ))}
))}

Emergency Response Plan

Immediate Actions

  1. Stay calm and assess the situation
  2. Call emergency services if needed
  3. Move to a safe location if possible
  4. Follow instructions from authorities

After the Incident

  1. Report the incident to authorities
  2. Document any evidence or details
  3. Seek support if needed
  4. Review and update your safety plan
); } export default SafetyTips;
